## 🔒 Security and Privacy

### Input Validation
- Message length limits (max 2000 characters)
- Content filtering for prohibited terms
- SQL injection prevention (no database queries)
- XSS prevention in API responses

### Rate Limiting
- IP-based rate limiting
- User-based rate limiting
- Exponential backoff for failures
- DOS protection

### Data Privacy
- Conversation context stored with TTL (72 hours default)
- No sensitive personal data stored
- Redis data can be encrypted at rest
- GDPR-friendly data handling

### Responsible Gaming Protection
- Automatic detection of concerning behavior
- Responsible gaming resource provision
- Strong disclaimers for vulnerable users
- Option to redirect to help resources

