## 📊 Monitoring and Observability

### Health Checks

```bash
# Check system health
curl http://localhost:8000/health

# Response
{
  "status": "healthy",
  "components": {
    "conversation_manager": "ok",
    "omega_control": "ok",
    "context_store": "redis"
  },
  "performance": {
    "total_responses": 1250,
    "average_response_time": 0.045,
    "error_rate": 0.2
  }
}
```

### Metrics and Logging

- **Structured logging** with JSON format
- **Performance metrics** (response time, error rate)
- **Conversation analytics** (intent distribution, user expertise)
- **Rate limiting metrics** (throttled requests, top IPs)

### Alerting Recommendations

- High error rate (>5%)
- Slow response times (>2 seconds average)
- Redis connection failures
- High rate limiting (>10% requests throttled)
- Responsible gaming triggers (for review)

